Class JavaService

java.lang.Object

io.atlasmap.service.ModuleService
io.atlasmap.java.service.JavaService
@Path("/java/") public class JavaService extends ModuleService
Java Service provides Java inspection service which generate an AtlasMap Document object from Java class.
